Core
- Pitch, produce, and script short original videos ( Experience/
- 3+ years experience in journalism/video production/social media content creation
- An excellent scriptwriter, producer, storyteller and collaborator, with strong interpersonal skills and experience in on-camera work;
- Existing source relationships with policy experts, labor leaders, advocacy organizations and other potential resources for finding leads and stories;
- Strong editorial judgement, understanding of journalistic practices and ethics, and experience working within a fast-paced cycle;
- The ability to manage multiple projects simultaneously and meet hard deadlines;
- Proven ability to grow audiences on social media is a plus, particularly for TikTok, Instagram, and YouTube;
- Passion for, and substantial knowledge of, national politics and economic justice issues;
- Available full-time hours and able to excel in a remote/work from home environment;
- Proficiency with Adobe Premiere as well as in-platform editing tools on TikTok and Instagram a plus;
- Experience managing interns or fellows is a plus;
- Experience producing and scripting YouTube content strongly desired At More Perfect Union we strive to increase diversity, equity, inclusion and justice in all elements of our work.

